---
layout: base.njk
title: "Heritage List"
---
<h1>Historical Monuments of Algiers</h1>
<p>Explore the architectural gems of the Casbah and beyond.</p>

<style>
    .monument-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .monument-card {
        background: white;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-left: 6px solid var(--terracotta);
        border-radius: 4px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .monument-card a {
        color: var(--hist-teal);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .monument-card a:hover { color: var(--med-blue); }
    .card-meta { color: var(--terracotta); font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; display: block; }
</style>

<ul class="monument-list">
{% for item in monuments %}
  <li class="monument-card">
    <span class="card-meta">{{ item.dynasty }} — {{ item.period }}</span>
    <a href="/algiers/monuments/{{ item.name | slugify }}/">{{ item.name }}</a>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #666;">{{ item.description }}</p>
  </li>

{% endfor %}
</ul>
